## Examples

```txt
feat(tokens): add brand layer to token pipeline
fix(cli): make registry source flags deterministic
test(registry): guard public api and template sync
refactor(ui): route components through semantic token classes
docs(tokens): document semantic size and spacing roles
docs(tokens): record dtcg output paths
chore(repo): add scoped package check scripts
feat(playground): add overlays QA panel
```

## Avoid

```txt
Normalize line height tokens
update: docs
feat: add TypeScript definitions for Dialog, Drawer, Menu...
fix(tests): formatting feat(tokens): ensure formatting
feat(button): add button
```
